clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學好d字點寫先上高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高登質素就係比你地班人拖低哂</blockquote><br />\nd你老母<br />\n尐呀！<br />\n學好尐字點寫先上<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連</span></span>登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&amp;gt;zi-&amp;gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&amp;gt;lit-&amp;gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。<br />\n<br />\n唔好衝出嚟柒得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0913457fa32247956013e1e724754599fca0237c","tid":38051,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"吾你老母 挽你老母"},{"pid":"9d0530fd7a5440653a80e3c882cd4db526471f31","tid":38051,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsP2f4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsP2f4i.jpg&h=153134e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95c45da0ca1f9e5fbc5190357a6b5b6b917f7fa8","tid":38051,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fa3d717d0db32a52776d8b2c79525a41c0916f8","tid":38051,"uid":13768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"多得呢個post我block左唔少5p mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論真心定假膠格殺勿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b72ff27a87f66fd689bddd6bc0951a5b368c489","tid":38051,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"086b8e34a40ddb8c8e9e877